{"tid":294560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"次撚次落雨都有呢啲傻閪","createTime":"2017-06-23T05:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T14:35:36.000Z","uid":123017,"like":18,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21e7cf3f3703a854012b687e35c38fafa7c411e3","tid":294560,"uid":123017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:14:51.000Z","msg":"頭先諗住落去買個老麥食啦點知見出面落雨就拎埋遮<br />\n發覺好多香港人一見落雨就做哂盲撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁落雨個個擔遮好正常啦<br />\n但點知前面迎面而來拎住遮既大媽準備同我擦身而過個陣<br />\n屌佢老尾佢舉高把遮喎，心諗:你矮撚過我舉乜尻姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成件事係好撚辛尻苦 又要搞到遮撞遮<br />\n之後我即刻用遮格硬撞柒翻佢先過到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚鐘意撞去玩碰碰車啦臭貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋好撚多盲撚係完全目中無人直撞直過唔撚會理人感受<br />\n而家嬲撚到一路食老麥一路打Post上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05797c417d65490bca73f66a5acc730fe0130bef","tid":294560,"uid":45185,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"好心矮撚就唔好出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee9f8048682fd310677292148c017f5c84511f0","tid":294560,"uid":31141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:16:18.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"b8140d88df1d76a6b505d9b3db7e8318b264ebae","tid":294560,"uid":123017,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心矮撚就唔好出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n矮唔撚緊要最緊要佢要學點擔遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.